sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant API as apps/server
  participant M as TemplateModule
  participant S as TemplateService
  participant DB as MySQL(template)

  API->>M: OnModuleInit
  M->>S: ensureDefaults()
  S->>DB: SELECT by key
  alt 不存在或版本落后
    S->>DB: UPSERT template(key,version,preset,...)
  end
  DB-->>S: ok

